data.description: *VA Assumable Loan for VA Buyers* 2.625% 30year fixed interest rate * This beautiful 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom home offers an ideal blend of comfort, convenience, and outdoor enjoyment. Surrounded by numerous parks, including a dedicated dog park and the scenic Water Tower Park, this location is a nature lover's dream. Inside, an open floor plan welcomes you with an abundance of natural light that fills the space. The main floor features gleaming hardwood laminate flooring, giving a warm and inviting feel to the entire home. The open kitchen is perfect for entertaining, with modern appliances and plenty of counter space for culinary creations. You’ll love how the beautiful hardwood railing accents the home's interior charm. As part of the HOA, you'll have full access to a refreshing pool and two well-equipped gyms, making daily exercise and relaxation a breeze. Not only is this home a tranquil retreat, but it's also incredibly convenient. Located just 20 minutes from Denver International Airport (DIA) and less than 30 minutes from downtown Denver, your connection to both work and leisure is effortlessly close. Don't miss this opportunity to call this Brighton gem your own. Schedule a showing today and discover your perfect home.
